      "updated": 1780666527278,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Constraints\n\n- 1 300 engineers\n- 1 200 services\n\n- Builds avg= 10 000 / day\n- Concurrent builds avg = 250 (10 working hours, 15min per  build)\n- Concurrent builds peak = 2000 \n- Worker nodes= 125 workers (64GB workers holding 16x4GB jobs)  ",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Constraints\n\n- 1 300 engineers\n- 1 200 services\n\n- Builds avg= 10 000 / day\n- Concurrent builds avg = 250 (10 working hours, 15min per  build)\n- Concurrent builds peak = 2000 \n- Worker nodes= 125 workers (64GB workers holding 16x4GB jobs)  ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
