      "versionNonce": 1579615313,
      "version": 48,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1780668219172,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "INTERVIEW TALKING POINTS\n\n• Build image ONCE → deploy by digest\n• Git = source of truth (GitOps)\n• Quality+security gates = fail-closed\n• Canary + SLO metrics → auto-rollback\n• Private clusters: pull agent, no inbound\n• Multi-region active-active + failover\n• Autoscale CI runners (KEDA) for spikes\n• RBAC + NetworkPolicy isolate teams",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "INTERVIEW TALKING POINTS\n\n• Build image ONCE → deploy by digest\n• Git = source of truth (GitOps)\n• Quality+security gates = fail-closed\n• Canary + SLO metrics → auto-rollback\n• Private clusters: pull agent, no inbound\n• Multi-region active-active + failover\n• Autoscale CI runners (KEDA) for spikes\n• RBAC + NetworkPolicy isolate teams",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 14,
      "index": "b2o",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "id": "JhaO2w1ulRDke85SwNVqf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -5029.830671480049,
      "y": -545.3477479503917,
      "width": 122.1107123238701,
      "height": 77.14285714285722,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
